title: Shia LaBeouf''s cryptic tweet post arrest
text:
Hollywood actor Shia LaBeouf has posted a cryptic message on Twitter after being arrested for public intoxication.
READ: Drunk Shia LaBeouf arrested for jaywalking in Austin
The 29-year-old Hollywood star was arrested for misdemeanour public intoxication outside a bar in Austin, Texas on Friday, and although he has not spoken out about the arrest, LaBeouf took to Twitter with a mysterious tweet, reported Access Hollywood.
Quote: : "I talk, just not to you."
This comes after an eyewitness claimed he "was either extremely drunk or high on drugs" and was running down the street before he started jaywalking in front of police officers.
The actor was out of control and disobeyed the officers.
The Transformers star - who was in Texas attending the Austin City Limits music festival - was subsequently handcuffed and taken to Travis County Jail.
